"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-katie-ledecky-is-chasing-her-own-greatness-paris-games-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t stop, won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t stop.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 41, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t stop\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 40}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to distill 12 years of unparalleled greatness to its essence, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s it.\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"12 years\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 73}, {\"ngram\": \"unparalleled greatness\", \"from\": 77, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"its essence\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even at the advanced swimming age of 27, she always wants to train, always wants to keep pushing, always is ready to grab the cap and goggles and do it again.\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the advanced swimming age\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 162}, {\"ngram\": \"the cap\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"goggles\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even a single week off, after an unbroken year of some of the hardest aerobic work possible, made her uncomfortable.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unbroken year\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest aerobic work\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It certainly wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t voluntary when she did it last year, despite all she had accomplished.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of athletes say they have no \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009coff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d switch; Ledecky legitimately lives that way.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"no \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009coff\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d switch\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's even added a solo Sunday swim to her routine, making her a seven-day-a-week swimmer.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a solo Sunday swim\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is that commitment to the grind a sign of compulsion or devotion?\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that commitment\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"the grind\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"a sign\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"compulsion\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"devotion\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps some of both.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Perhaps some\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s affection for swimming is real, as her new memoir makes clear.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s affection\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"her new memoir\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a sport rife with burnout, she is the eternal flame.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport rife\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"burnout\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the eternal flame\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED:Meet Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Roster for the 2024 Paris Olympics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI can tell you, she wants to swim forever,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says her coach at Gator Swim Club, Anthony Nesty.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Nesty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Nesty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meet Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Roster\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"Gator Swim Club\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBecause she enjoys it so much.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d She enjoys it enough to have built her entire lifestyle around it.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her entire lifestyle\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early to bed, early to rise, a healthy eater, a non-partier, a limited romantic life, immune to social drama\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094all of it requires an unusual level of focus, but Ledecky has never seen that as a sacrifice.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"a healthy eater\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"partier\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"a limited romantic life\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"social drama\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094all\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"an unusual level\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"focus\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"a sacrifice\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s simply who she is and what it takes for her to do her best in what she loves most.\\u00c2 What she does is incredibly hard, but why she succeeds is also incredibly simple.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"simply who\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She puts in the work, in every facet of her life.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"every facet\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she puts in the work because she loves it.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis Olympicswill be Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fourth Summer Games.She wants to shoot for a fifth, on home soil (in home water?\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheParis Olympicswill\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"fourth Summer Games\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"home soil\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"home water\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"), in Los Angeles four years from now.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.654743716084622e-29, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That would equal Michael Phelps\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s five, and although she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll never match his 23 gold medals and 28 overall medals, she could do him one better by winning a medal in all five of her Olympics.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"his 23 gold medals\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"28 overall medals\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympics\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Phelps did not win one at his first Summer Games in 2000.)\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7069982201013143e-16, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Summer Games\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky has won gold as an anonymous teen in London, gold as an unbeatable giant in Rio de Janeiro and gold as a 24-year-old facing greater competition in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.036226628870922e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.612993782900596e-28, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.997877701542266, \"rank\": 0.002126812186708858, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"an anonymous teen\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"an unbeatable giant\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"a 24-year-old facing greater competition\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s won seven Olympic gold medals total\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and she will win more in Paris.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.69911911555074e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"seven Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the prohibitive favorite in the 1,500-meter freestyle and a solid favorite in the 800, not to mention a strong medal threat in the 400 and the 4X200 freestyle relay.\\u00c2 A host of new milestones for long-term excellence are within reach.\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prohibitive favorite\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"a solid favorite\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong medal threat\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4X200 freestyle relay\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"A host\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"new milestones\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"long-term excellence\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two more golds would break American Jenny Thompson\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s record for the most by a female swimmer and tie the record for most by a female Olympian (Russian gymnast Larisa Latynina).\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999971691735532, \"rank\": 2.830356475869952e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2579, \"end\": 2584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\", \"score\": 0.9709684216305913, \"rank\": 0.025084642290254353, \"text\": \"Jenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\"}, {\"begin\": 2688, \"end\": 2695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9668403300857557, \"rank\": 0.029688096248537837, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two more golds\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"a female swimmer\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three more medals of any kind would give her 13, breaking the American female record of 12 held by Thompson and Dara Torres.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2784, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999971691735532, \"rank\": 2.830356475869952e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2821, \"end\": 2829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9756186846446046, \"rank\": 0.024990619531382728, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dara Torres\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Three more medals\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a victory in the 800-meter freestyle, she can become the first woman to win four straight Olympic gold medals in the same event.\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"the first woman\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"four straight Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"the same event\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So many big moments have already been achieved, with more to come.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"So many big moments\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the smaller, daily moments that create her satisfaction.\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And yet it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"the smaller, daily moments\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"her satisfaction\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone who knows Ledecky will say she relishes practice more than the competitions.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3130}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s despite the fact that swim practice is a grueling, largely solitary endeavor.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"swim practice\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"a grueling, largely solitary endeavor\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spending hours face-down, staring at a black line, communication coming only with gasping breaths between efforts\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not terribly 