anford\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adulthood and professional swimming\", \"from\": 10272, \"to\": 10307}, {\"ngram\": \"most recent world record\", \"from\": 10321, \"to\": 10345}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500 freestyle\", \"from\": 10350, \"to\": 10369}, {\"ngram\": \"her first pro meet\", \"from\": 10385, \"to\": 10403}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 10420, \"to\": 10432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She appreciates that Nesty connected on a personal level and dared to fine-tune her stroke\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which he described as \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cchoppy\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cinefficient\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in an attempt to make the greatest distance swimmer better.\", \"from\": 10434, \"to\": 10645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nesty\", \"from\": 10455, \"to\": 10460}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal level\", \"from\": 10474, \"to\": 10490}, {\"ngram\": \"fine-tune\", \"from\": 10504, \"to\": 10513}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 10589, \"to\": 10599}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest distance swimmer\", \"from\": 10608, \"to\": 10637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly, though, Ledecky writes bouquets to the sport itself.\", \"from\": 10647, \"to\": 10707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 10663, \"to\": 10670}, {\"ngram\": \"bouquets\", \"from\": 10678, \"to\": 10686}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 10690, \"to\": 10699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s impossible to do what she has done at the highest level for 12 years\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094to swim some of the hardest events, which require the most grueling practices\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094without deriving joy from it.\", \"from\": 10708, \"to\": 10895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u00