\u0099s game, especially on the female side.\", \"from\": 11260, \"to\": 11402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11268, \"end\": 11281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\"}, {\"begin\": 11328, \"end\": 11333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.69911911555074e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 11335, \"end\": 11343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.823795253107422e-27, \"text\": \"Swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Swiss-Army Knife\", \"from\": 11295, \"to\": 11324}, {\"ngram\": \"a young person\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s game\", \"from\": 11346, \"to\": 11369}, {\"ngram\": \"the female side\", \"from\": 11385, \"to\": 11400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ledecky has evolved from phenom to terminator to elder stateswoman (and U.S. team captain) without losing much at all.\", \"from\": 11403, \"to\": 11525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 11407, \"to\": 11414}, {\"ngram\": \"phenom\", \"from\": 11432, \"to\": 11438}, {\"ngram\": \"elder stateswoman\", \"from\": 11456, \"to\": 11473}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. team captain\", \"from\": 11479, \"to\": 11496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s one of the few star swimmers who has never had an existential crisis that threatened to drive her from the sport.\", \"from\": 11526, \"to\": 11647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00