s emptied into a pool at the end of a season, and then the emotions come forth.\", \"from\": 11966, \"to\": 12073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s worth\", \"from\": 11966, \"to\": 11982}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 11986, \"to\": 11990}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 12009, \"to\": 12015}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 12019, \"to\": 12026}, {\"ngram\": \"a season\", \"from\": 12030, \"to\": 12038}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 12049, \"to\": 12061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI sometimes feel depleted after end-of-season meets,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ledecky writes in her book.\", \"from\": 12075, \"to\": 12161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"season\", \"from\": 12117, \"to\": 12123}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 12134, \"to\": 12141}, {\"ngram\": \"her book\", \"from\": 12152, \"to\": 12160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI have so much tension built inside of me.\", \"from\": 12162, \"to\": 12207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much tension\", \"from\": 12172, \"to\": 12187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the meet ends, I take my first deep breath in months.\", \"from\": 12208, \"to\": 12266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the meet\", \"from\": 12213, \"to\": 12221}, {\"ngram\": \"my first deep breath\", \"from\": 12235, \"to\": 12255}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 12259, \"to\": 12265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s this emotional release after being laser-focused and locked down for such a long period of time.\", \"from\": 12267, \"to\": 12373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s this emotional release\", \"from\": 12267, \"to\": 12299}, {\"ngram\": \"such a long period\", \"from\": 12346, \"to\": 12364}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 12368, \"to\": 12372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t control it.\", \"from\": 12374, \"to\": 12395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I deflate like a balloon.\", \"from\": 12396, \"to\": 12421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a balloon\", \"from\": 12411, \"to\": 12420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I get in my feelings.\\\"\", \"from\": 12422, \"to\": 12444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my feelings\", \"from\": 12431, \"to\": 12442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It cannot be easy chasing her own greatness, trying to replicate world records set years ago.\", \"from\": 12446, \"to\": 12539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own greatness\", \"from\": 12472, \"to\": 12489}, {\"ngram\": \"world records\", \"from\": 12511, \"to\": 12524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s especially challenging when the rest of the world has gotten faster, trying to clear the bar Ledecky raised so high.\", \"from\": 12540, \"to\": 12663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 12540, \"to\": 12546}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 12575, \"to\": 12583}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 12587, \"to\": 12596}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 12632, \"to\": 12639}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 12640, \"to\": 12647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But out of respect for swimming and love of the water, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s still giving it everything she has, every single day.\", \"from\": 12664, \"to\": 12780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 12675, \"to\": 12682}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 12687, \"to\": 12695}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 12700, \"to\": 12704}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 12708, \"to\": 12717}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 12743, \"to\": 12753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without a doctor or coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s orders, Katie Ledecky can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t stop and won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t stop.\", \"from\": 12782, \"to\": 12864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\"